column5: Dont know. Did you eat it? Lol. I think its an arctic char.
Doesn't have the typical char vermiculations, so I'll take a wild stab and say male cutt-bow in full spawning dress.
LOL you mean red snapper was wrong?
Looks like his buddies just gave him a pink belly.  JF
Thats there is one purdy fish ! And yes I would have said a cross between a Bow and a Speck ... but without the typical leading white (char-line) on the fins ... cutt-bow would be my guess too.
